      "updated": 1771442584649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Neurology_Lakehouse\nEnable onelake security and user \nidentity.  Otherwise, the access of the user\nwho setup the shortcut will be used (delegated identity)\nand this may expose more data than desired.\nUsing user identity will enforce RLS/CLS of the roles\napplied in the source lakehouse (Data_Lakehouse)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Neurology_Lakehouse\nEnable onelake security and user \nidentity.  Otherwise, the access of the user\nwho setup the shortcut will be used (delegated identity)\nand this may expose more data than desired.\nUsing user identity will enforce RLS/CLS of the roles\napplied in the source lakehouse (Data_Lakehouse)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
